typeProperties.script:
source(output(
		EmployeeKey as integer,
		ParentEmployeeKey as string,
		EmployeeNationalIDAlternateKey as string,
		ParentEmployeeNationalIDAlternateKey as string,
		SalesTerritoryKey as string,
		FirstName as string,
		LastName as string,
		MiddleName as string,
		NameStyle as string,
		Title as string,
		HireDate as string,
		BirthDate as string,
		LoginID as string,
		EmailAddress as string,
		Phone as string,
		MaritalStatus as string,
		EmergencyContactName as string,
		EmergencyContactPhone as string,
		SalariedFlag as string,
		Gender as string,
		PayFrequency as string,
		BaseRate as string,
		VacationHours as string,
		SickLeaveHours as string,
		CurrentFlag as string,
		SalesPersonFlag as string,
		DepartmentName as string,
		StartDate as string,
		EndDate as string,
		Status as string,
		EmployeePhoto as string
	),
	allowSchemaDrift: true,
	validateSchema: false,
	ignoreNoFilesFound: false,
	inferDriftedColumnTypes: true) ~> RAWEmployee
source(output(
		ProductKey as integer,
		ProductAlternateKey as string,
		ProductSubcategoryKey as integer,
		WeightUnitMeasureCode as string,
		SizeUnitMeasureCode as string,
		EnglishProductName as string,
		SpanishProductName as string,
		FrenchProductName as string,
		StandardCost as string,
		FinishedGoodsFlag as string,
		Color as string,
		SafetyStockLevel as string,
		ReorderPoint as string,
		ListPrice as string,
		Size as string,
		SizeRange as string,
		Weight as string,
		DaysToManufacture as string,
		ProductLine as string,
		DealerPrice as string,
		Class as string,
		Style as string,
		ModelName as string,
		LargePhoto as string,
		EnglishDescription as string,
		FrenchDescription as string,
		ChineseDescription as string,
		ArabicDescription as string,
		HebrewDescription as string,
		ThaiDescription as string,
		GermanDescription as string,
		JapaneseDescription as string,
		TurkishDescription as string,
		StartDate as string,
		EndDate as string,
		Status as string
	),
	allowSchemaDrift: true,
	validateSchema: false,
	ignoreNoFilesFound: false,
	inferDriftedColumnTypes: true) ~> RAWProduct
source(output(
		ProductCategoryKey as integer,
		ProductCategoryAlternateKey as string,
		EnglishProductCategoryName as string,
		SpanishProductCategoryName as string,
		FrenchProductCategoryName as string
	),
	allowSchemaDrift: true,
	validateSchema: false,
	ignoreNoFilesFound: false,
	inferDriftedColumnTypes: true) ~> RAWProductCategory
source(output(
		ProductSubcategoryKey as integer,
		ProductSubcategoryAlternateKey as string,
		EnglishProductSubcategoryName as string,
		SpanishProductSubcategoryName as string,
		FrenchProductSubcategoryName as string,
		ProductCategoryKey as integer
	),
	allowSchemaDrift: true,
	validateSchema: false,
	ignoreNoFilesFound: false,
	inferDriftedColumnTypes: true) ~> RAWProductSubcategory
source(output(
		SalesTerritoryKey as string,
		SalesTerritoryAlternateKey as string,
		SalesTerritoryRegion as string,
		SalesTerritoryCountry as string,
		SalesTerritoryGroup as string,
		SalesTerritoryImage as string
	),
	allowSchemaDrift: true,
	validateSchema: true,
	ignoreNoFilesFound: false,
	inferDriftedColumnTypes: true) ~> RAWSalesTerritory
source(output(
		ProductKey as integer,
		OrderDateKey as date,
		DueDateKey as string,
		ShipDateKey as date,
		ResellerKey as integer,
		EmployeeKey as integer,
		PromotionKey as string,
		CurrencyKey as string,
		SalesTerritoryKey as string,
		SalesOrderNumber as string,
		SalesOrderLineNumber as string,
		RevisionNumber as string,
		OrderQuantity as decimal(10,0),
		UnitPrice as string,
		ExtendedAmount as string,
		UnitPriceDiscountPct as string,
		DiscountAmount as string,
		ProductStandardCost as string,
		TotalProductCost as decimal(10,0),
		SalesAmount as decimal(10,0),
		TaxAmt as string,
		Freight as string,
		CarrierTrackingNumber as string,
		CustomerPONumber as string,
		OrderDate as string,
		DueDate as string,
		ShipDate as string
	),
	allowSchemaDrift: true,
	validateSchema: false,
	ignoreNoFilesFound: false,
	inferDriftedColumnTypes: true) ~> RAWResellerSales
source(output(
		SalesQuotaKey as string,
		EmployeeKey as integer,
		DateKey as date,
		CalendarYear as string,
		CalendarQuarter as string,
		SalesAmountQuota as decimal(10,0),
		Date as string
	),
	allowSchemaDrift: true,
	validateSchema: false,
	ignoreNoFilesFound: false,
	inferDriftedColumnTypes: true) ~> RAWSalesQuota
source(output(
		ResellerKey as integer,
		GeographyKey as integer,
		ResellerAlternateKey as string,
		Phone as string,
		BusinessType as string,
		ResellerName as string,
		NumberEmployees as string,
		OrderFrequency as string,
		OrderMonth as string,
		FirstOrderYear as string,
		LastOrderYear as string,
		ProductLine as string,
		AddressLine1 as string,
		AddressLine2 as string,
		AnnualSales as string,
		BankName as string,
		MinPaymentType as string,
		MinPaymentAmount as string,
		AnnualRevenue as string,
		YearOpened as string
	),
	allowSchemaDrift: true,
	validateSchema: false,
	ignoreNoFilesFound: false,
	inferDriftedColumnTypes: true) ~> RAWReseller
source(output(
		GeographyKey as integer,
		City as string,
		StateProvinceCode as string,
		StateProvinceName as string,
		CountryRegionCode as string,
		EnglishCountryRegionName as string,
		SpanishCountryRegionName as string,
		FrenchCountryRegionName as string,
		PostalCode as string,
		SalesTerritoryKey as string,
		IpAddressLocator as string
	),
	allowSchemaDrift: true,
	validateSchema: false,
	ignoreNoFilesFound: false,
	inferDriftedColumnTypes: true) ~> RAWGeography
source(output(
		DateKey as date,
		FullDateAlternateKey as date,
		DayNumberOfWeek as string,
		EnglishDayNameOfWeek as string,
		SpanishDayNameOfWeek as string,
		FrenchDayNameOfWeek as string,
		DayNumberOfMonth as string,
		DayNumberOfYear as string,
		WeekNumberOfYear as string,
		EnglishMonthName as string,
		SpanishMonthName as string,
		FrenchMonthName as string,
		MonthNumberOfYear as integer,
		CalendarQuarter as integer,
		CalendarYear as integer,
		CalendarSemester as string,
		FiscalQuarter as string,
		FiscalYear as string,
		FiscalSemester as string
	),
	allowSchemaDrift: true,
	validateSchema: false,
	ignoreNoFilesFound: false,
	inferDriftedColumnTypes: true) ~> RAWDate
source(output(
		ProductCategoryKey as integer,
		ProductCategoryAlternateKey as string,
		EnglishProductCategoryName as string,
		SpanishProductCategoryName as string,
		FrenchProductCategoryName as string
	),
	allowSchemaDrift: true,
	validateSchema: false,
	ignoreNoFilesFound: false,
	inferDriftedColumnTypes: true) ~> RAWProductCategorySubCat
RAWEmployee derive(FullName = FirstName + " " + LastName) ~> RawEmployeeDerived
RawEmployeeDerived filter(SalesPersonFlag == "True") ~> RawEmployeeFiltered
RawEmployeeFiltered select(mapColumn(
		EmployeeKey,
		SalesTerritoryKey,
		FirstName,
		LastName,
		LoginID,
		FullName
	),
	skipDuplicateMapInputs: true,
	skipDuplicateMapOutputs: true) ~> RawEmployeeSelected
RAWProduct filter(FinishedGoodsFlag == "True") ~> RawProductFiltered
RawProductFiltered select(mapColumn(
		ProductKey,
		ProductSubcategoryKey,
		EnglishProductName,
		Color
	),
	skipDuplicateMapInputs: true,
	skipDuplicateMapOutputs: true) ~> RawProductSelected
RAWProductCategory select(mapColumn(
		ProductCategoryKey,
		EnglishProductCategoryName
	),
	skipDuplicateMapInputs: true,
	skipDuplicateMapOutputs: true) ~> RawProductCategorySelected
RAWProductSubcategory select(mapColumn(
		ProductSubcategoryKey,
		EnglishProductSubcategoryName,
		ProductCategoryKey
	),
	skipDuplicateMapInputs: true,
	skipDuplicateMapOutputs: true) ~> RawProductSubcategorySelected
RAWSalesTerritory select(mapColumn(
		SalesTerritoryKey,
		SalesTerritoryRegion,
		SalesTerritoryCountry,
		SalesTerritoryGroup
	),
	skipDuplicateMapInputs: true,
	skipDuplicateMapOutputs: true) ~> RawSalesTerritorySelected
RAWResellerSales select(mapColumn(
		ProductKey,
		OrderDateKey,
		ShipDateKey,
		ResellerKey,
		EmployeeKey,
		SalesTerritoryKey,
		OrderQuantity,
		TotalProductCost,
		SalesAmount
	),
	skipDuplicateMapInputs: true,
	skipDuplicateMapOutputs: true) ~> RawResellerSalesSelected
RAWSalesQuota select(mapColumn(
		EmployeeKey,
		DateKey,
		SalesAmountQuota
	),
	skipDuplicateMapInputs: true,
	skipDuplicateMapOutputs: true) ~> RawSalesQuotaSelected
RAWReseller select(mapColumn(
		ResellerKey,
		BusinessType,
		ResellerName,
		GeographyKey
	),
	skipDuplicateMapInputs: true,
	skipDuplicateMapOutputs: true) ~> RawResellerSelected
RAWGeography select(mapColumn(
		EnglishCountryRegionName,
		StateProvinceName,
		City,
		GeographyKey
	),
	skipDuplicateMapInputs: true,
	skipDuplicateMapOutputs: true) ~> RawGeographySelected
RAWDate select(mapColumn(
		DateKey,
		FullDateAlternateKey,
		MonthNumberOfYear,
		CalendarQuarter,
		CalendarYear
	),
	skipDuplicateMapInputs: true,
	skipDuplicateMapOutputs: true) ~> RawDateSelected
RawResellerSalesJoinSelected derive(Country = "USA",
		UnitCostAmount = TotalProductCost / OrderQuantity,
		ProductName = EnglishProductName) ~> RawResellerSalesDerived
RawResellerSalesSelected, RawProductSelected join(RawResellerSalesSelected@ProductKey == RawProductSelected@ProductKey,
	joinType:'left',
	broadcast: 'auto')~> RawResellerSalesProductJoin
RawResellerSalesProductJoin select(mapColumn(
		ProductKey = RawResellerSalesSelected@ProductKey,
		OrderDateKey,
		ShipDateKey,
		ResellerKey,
		EmployeeKey,
		SalesTerritoryKey,
		OrderQuantity,
		TotalProductCost,
		SalesAmount,
		ProductKey = RawProductSelected@ProductKey,
		EnglishProductName
	),
	skipDuplicateMapInputs: true,
	skipDuplicateMapOutputs: true) ~> RawResellerSalesJoinSelected
RawResellerSalesDerived select(mapColumn(
		ProductKey,
		OrderDateKey,
		ShipDateKey,
		ResellerKey,
		EmployeeKey,
		SalesTerritoryKey,
		OrderQuantity,
		TotalProductCost,
		SalesAmount,
		Country,
		UnitCostAmount,
		ProductName
	),
	skipDuplicateMapInputs: true,
	skipDuplicateMapOutputs: true) ~> RemoveColumns1
RAWProductCategorySubCat, RAWProductSubcategory join(RAWProductCategorySubCat@ProductCategoryKey == RAWProductSubcategory@ProductCategoryKey,
	joinType:'inner',
	broadcast: 'auto')~> ProductCategorySubCat
RawEmployeeSelected sink(allowSchemaDrift: true,
	validateSchema: false,
	skipDuplicateMapInputs: true,
	skipDuplicateMapOutputs: true) ~> RawEmployeeSink
RawProductSelected sink(allowSchemaDrift: true,
	validateSchema: false,
	skipDuplicateMapInputs: true,
	skipDuplicateMapOutputs: true) ~> RamProductSink
RawProductCategorySelected sink(allowSchemaDrift: true,
	validateSchema: false,
	skipDuplicateMapInputs: true,
	skipDuplicateMapOutputs: true) ~> RawProductCategorySink
RawProductSubcategorySelected sink(allowSchemaDrift: true,
	validateSchema: false,
	skipDuplicateMapInputs: true,
	skipDuplicateMapOutputs: true) ~> RawProductSubcategorySink
RemoveColumns1 sink(allowSchemaDrift: true,
	validateSchema: false,
	skipDuplicateMapInputs: true,
	skipDuplicateMapOutputs: true) ~> RawResellerSalesSink
RawSalesQuotaSelected sink(allowSchemaDrift: true,
	validateSchema: false,
	skipDuplicateMapInputs: true,
	skipDuplicateMapOutputs: true) ~> RawSalesQuotaSink
RawResellerSelected sink(allowSchemaDrift: true,
	validateSchema: false,
	skipDuplicateMapInputs: true,
	skipDuplicateMapOutputs: true) ~> RawResellerSink
RawGeographySelected sink(allowSchemaDrift: true,
	validateSchema: false,
	skipDuplicateMapInputs: true,
	skipDuplicateMapOutputs: true) ~> RawGeographySink
RawDateSelected sink(allowSchemaDrift: true,
	validateSchema: false,
	skipDuplicateMapInputs: true,
	skipDuplicateMapOutputs: true) ~> RawDateSink
RawSalesTerritorySelected sink(allowSchemaDrift: true,
	validateSchema: false,
	skipDuplicateMapInputs: true,
	skipDuplicateMapOutputs: true) ~> RawSalesTerritorySink
ProductCategorySubCat sink(allowSchemaDrift: true,
	validateSchema: false,
	skipDuplicateMapInputs: true,
	skipDuplicateMapOutputs: true) ~> RawProductCategorySubCatSink
